Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: fortunes-lab
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, fortune-mod
Description: bioinformatics fortune cookies for the fortune(6) program
 A fortune cookie pack tailored to bioinformatics labs: equal parts
 hard-won lab humour, real quotes from biology, statistics and computing,
 and quotes collected from local professors and PIs.
 .
 Installs the data files lab, lab-quotes and lab-local (with their
 compiled .dat indexes) under /usr/share/games/fortunes, ready for use with
 the fortune(6) program, e.g. "fortune lab".
